fields.description:
Steps to Reproduce:
1. Run KS on 4.2 Emulator

Actual:
Lots of warn/error messages displaying in console, see attached log

Expected:
Not to get all these warning and error message
fields.summary: Android: 4.2 Emulator is displaying a lot of error/warn messages when running KS
fields.environment:
Android 4.2 Emulator
SDK: 2.1.4.GA, 3.0.0.v20121112163159
Titanium Studio, build: 2.1.2.201208301612

comments.body:
It happens whether or not any application (Titanium or native) is running.

Here is pastie of me simply running the emulator (from Android's own AVD manager):

http://pastie.org/5374382

We can't do anything about this.  It's unrelated to Titanium.
